<blog-post>
	<blog-title>First blog post</blog-title>
	<blog-content>
		<tab></tab>This is my very first blog post after creating this repository. This blog describes how every other blog post will be created. 
		<ul>
			<li>Clone the repository.</li>
			<li>In the &lt;REPO_HOME&gt;/content/blog directory, create a new blog post with the file name same as the one that will appear in the URL.</li>
			<li>The post must be enclosed within &lt;blog-post&gt;&lt;/blog-post&gt; tag.</li>
			<li>The title must be enclose in &lt;blog-title&gt;&lt;/blog-title&gt; tag.</li>
			<li>The content must be enclosed in &lt;blog-content&gt;&lt;/blog-content&gt; tag.</li>
			<li>Go to &lt;REPO_HOME&gt;. Run the build.py python script with &lt;REPO_HOME&gt; as the current working directory.</li>
			<li>Push your changes in the repository.</li>
		</ul>
	</blog-content>
</blog-post>